'''Kevin J. McManus''' (born November 3, 1978 in [[Kansas City, Missouri]]) is an American attorney<ref>{{cite web|title=Law Office of Kevin McManus|url=http://www.kevinmcmanuslaw.com}}</ref> and politician from the state of [[Missouri]]. He was elected the [[Missouri House of Representatives]] in 2010 and was re-elected in 2012 and 2014.<ref>{{cite web|title=Ballotpedia, Kevin McManus|url=https://ballotpedia.org/Kevin_McManus}}</ref> In 2015, he was elected to the City Council of Kansas City, Missouri,<ref>{{cite web|title=Kansas City Star | url=http://www.kansascity.com/news/politics-government/election/article25379818.html}}</ref> where he presently serves <ref>{{cite web|title=City of Kansas City, Councilman Kevin McManus | url=http://www.kcmo.gov/mcmanus}}</ref>.
